{"tid":1161010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[25仔下場]  中情局前探員售美國國防機密予中國　判囚20年","createTime":"2019-05-19T00:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T08:00:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a04aace35b5385fa0020774dd5068cd84241a4","tid":1161010,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T00:14:54.000Z","msg":"中情局前探員售美國國防機密予中國　判囚20年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190518/s00004/1558150686903/%e4%b8%ad%e6%83%85%e5%b1%80%e5%89%8d%e6%8e%a2%e5%93%a1%e5%94%ae%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%9c%8b%e9%98%b2%e6%a9%9f%e5%af%86%e4%ba%88%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b-%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a20%e5%b9%b4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190518%2Fs00004%2F1558150686903%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25b1%2580%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%258e%25a2%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%2594%25ae%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25af%2586%25e4%25ba%2588%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b-%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a20%25e5%25b9%25b4&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=6bdab080\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190518%2Fs00004%2F1558150686903%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25b1%2580%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%258e%25a2%25e5%2593%25a1%25e5%2594%25ae%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%2598%25b2%25e6%25a9%259f%25e5%25af%2586%25e4%25ba%2588%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b-%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a20%25e5%25b9%25b4&h=4fa24051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190518/s00004/1558150686903/%e4%b8%ad%e6%83%85%e5%b1%80%e5%89%8d%e6%8e%a2%e5%93%a1%e5%94%ae%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%9c%8b%e9%98%b2%e6%a9%9f%e5%af%86%e4%ba%88%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b-%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a20%e5%b9%b4</a><br />\n<br />\n美國中央情報局（CIA）前探員馬洛里（Kevin Patrick Mallory），被指控替中國從事間諜活動，泄露美國國防機密，周五（17日）被判刑20年。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部助理部長德默斯（John Demers）周五發聲明表示，美國情報官員遭中國鎖定為目標而背叛國家和同僚，已成為令人警戒的趨勢，今次案件是其中一個案例。<br />\n<br />\n居住弗吉尼亞州利斯堡（Leesburg）的馬洛里，被控在2017年4月前往中國上海時，以2.5萬美元向中國情報人員出售機密的美國國防資料，和向調查人員作假口供，去年6月被裁定多項罪名成立。<br />\n<br />\n62歲的馬洛里能說流利中文，曾在美國軍中服役，也曾擔任國務院安全部門的特別探員，之後到中情局擔任秘密案件專員，能接觸最高機密資料。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局（FBI）特工在馬洛里從上海帶回的通訊設備上，發現列為「最高機密」及「秘密」的文件，以及顯示其違法的短訊後，控告他替中國從事間諜活動，違反間諜法（Espionage Act）。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/法新社/紐約時報）"},{"pid":"2f9e36a989e0f99b43d8fc5bf000e0b2eb905862","tid":1161010,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T00:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23351dd686867c5a08846bb6e525f884acb76be","tid":1161010,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e32170aebfe6f52b3d1f669d0cbd055e02a2c60","tid":1161010,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe6bd9c36d84cd7cd8baa4874f7cac51384a163","tid":1161010,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"62歲判廿年，人生都完結"},{"pid":"a06dad194fa8cdc307f762e7644485c4ccd9bc67","tid":1161010,"uid":186443,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"2.5 萬咁鬼死平嘅？"},{"pid":"55a11035db63945c9e1c0e157efdb631552b8089","tid":1161010,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a06dad194fa8cdc307f762e7644485c4ccd9bc67","tid":1161010,"uid":186443,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"2.5 萬咁鬼死平嘅？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:44:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔做兩蚊都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c8cf15d74df495f